      "author": "SntTGR",
      "description": "- Description column revamp\r\n    - Added support for links inside description\r\n    - Added support for description column types (oneline, multiline, count, truncate, etc)\r\n- Annotation support\r\n    - Support for links and file previews in annotations (similar to taskopen/tasknotes)\r\n        - files can be relative to vault, to home and absolute. Only links that pertain to the vault are highlighted and preview'd\r\n    - Adding and removing notes via a new annotations and the modify task modals\r\n- Integration for tasknote and taskopen    \r\n\r\n<img width=\"740\" height=\"935\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ac76534b-7a0c-4230-bab7-695f53820fb9\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* Add tasknote integration by @oliverarkenklo-hue in https://github.com/SntTGR/obsidian-tw-task-wiki/pull/10\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @oliverarkenklo-hue made their first contribution in https://github.com/SntTGR/obsidian-tw-task-wiki/pull/10\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/SntTGR/obsidian-tw-task-wiki/compare/1.2.1...1.3.0",
